that don't require gasoline.

976
00:51:20,208 --> 00:51:25,458
You sucked the gas out
of my arm chainsaws while I was sleeping?

977
00:51:25,541 --> 00:51:28,958
Jesus Christ,
what kind of psychopath are you?

978
00:51:29,041 --> 00:51:31,375
The worst kind.

979
