1159
01:00:22,625 --> 01:00:25,375
Guys, you have got to see this. Look.

1160
01:00:25,458 --> 01:00:26,750
Whoa!

1161
01:00:26,833 --> 01:00:27,875
What do you see?

1162
01:00:27,958 --> 01:00:30,208
